FB_TOS_Digi_1920x1080.png"><media:title>2026 FB Mini-packs and Parking</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/7/10/26FB_TOS_Digi_1920x1080.png" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Fri, 10 Jul 2026 11:02:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>2</s:sport_id><s:story_id>59236</s:story_id></item><item><title>WVU-Auburn Game Time Set, Tickets on Sale This Week for Players Era 8</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/7/13/mens-basketball-wvu-auburn-game-time-set-tickets-on-sale-this-week-for-players-era-8</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/7/13/mens-basketball-wvu-auburn-game-time-set-tickets-on-sale-this-week-for-players-era-8</guid><category>Men's Basketball</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="The game time has been set for the WVU-Auburn game in Las Vegas" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/7/13/MBB26_PEAuburnGameTime_1920x1080.jpg" /><br /><br />NEW YORK/LAS VEGAS – Players Era, an EverWonder Studio company, and MGM Resorts International today announced that tickets for the Players Era Men's Basketball Championships will go on sale this week, with pre-sales starting Thursday, July 16 at 10 a.m. PST, and the public on-sale Friday, July 17 at 10 a.m. PST.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/7/13/MBB26_PEAuburnGameTime_1920x1080.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/7/13/MBB26_PEAuburnGameTime_1920x1080.jpg"><media:title>The game time has been set for the WVU-Auburn game in Las Vegas</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/7/13/MBB26_PEAuburnGameTime_1920x1080.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jul 2026 10:56:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>4</s:sport_id><s:story_id>59240</s:story_id></item><item><title>Bassinger Agrees to Deal With Blue Jays</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/7/13/baseball-bassinger-agrees-to-deal-with-blue-jays</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/7/13/baseball-bassinger-agrees-to-deal-with-blue-jays</guid><category>Baseball</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="Reese Bassinger throws a pitch against North Carolina in the College World Series" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/7/13/EEN08447_large.jpg" /><br /><br />MORGANTOWN, W.Va. – Pitcher Reese Bassinger of the West Virginia University baseball team has signed an undrafted free agent contract with the Toronto Blue Jays.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/7/13/EEN08447_large.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/7/13/EEN08447_large.jpg"><media:title>Reese Bassinger throws a pitch against North Carolina in the College World Series</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/7/13/EEN08447_large.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jul 2026 10:51:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>1</s:sport_id><s:story_id>59239</s:story_id></item><item><title>Schoenfeld, Korn Selected on Day 2 of MLB Draft</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/7/12/baseball-schoenfeld-korn-selected-on-day-2-of-mlb-draft</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/7/12/baseball-schoenfeld-korn-selected-on-day-2-of-mlb-draft</guid><category>Baseball</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="Paul Schoenfeld, Ian Korn" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/7/12/Untitled-1Draft_Day_2.jpg" /><br /><br />MORGANTOWN, W.Va. – Outfielder Paul Schoenfeld and pitcher Ian Korn of the West Virginia University baseball team were selected in the 2026 MLB Draft on Sunday. Schoenfeld was drafted by the Arizona Diamondbacks in the eighth round with the 236th overall pick while Korn went in the 10th round to the San Francisco Giants with the 298th overall pick.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/7/12/Untitled-1Draft_Day_2.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/7/12/Untitled-1Draft_Day_2.jpg"><media:title>Paul Schoenfeld, Ian Korn</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/7/12/Untitled-1Draft_Day_2.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Sun, 12 Jul 2026 19:05:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>1</s:sport_id><s:story_id>59238</s:story_id></item><item><title>Montesa, Yehl Selected on Day 1 of MLB Draft</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/7/11/baseball-montesa-yehl-selected-on-day-1-of-mlb-draft</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/7/11/baseball-montesa-yehl-selected-on-day-1-of-mlb-draft</guid><category>Baseball</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="Dawson Montesa, Maxx Yehl" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/7/11/Untitled-1Montesa__Yeh.jpg" /><br /><br />MORGANTOWN, W.Va. – West Virginia University pitchers Dawson Montesa and Maxx Yehl became the latest Mountaineers to be selected in the MLB Draft on Saturday. Montesa was taken by the St. Louis Cardinals in the Competi